{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to Arcade Galaxy!</strong> Step into a creative universe where you design, share, and conquer your own 3D platformer levels. Take control of lovable animal characters called <i>Cubs</i> as you explore countless user-generated maps, each filled with unique challenges and surprises. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/explosion1.png?t=1735796284\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Arcade Galaxy</strong> is all about unleashing your creativity! Use our intuitive level editor to build the platforming experience of your dreams. Create thrilling obstacles, clever traps, and custom gameplay rules with an easy-to-use visual logic editor. Whether it\u2019s crafting devilishly tricky jumps or designing the perfect run-through for others to beat, the power to shape the galaxy is in your hands. Once complete, share your creations with players worldwide and test their skills on your maps.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/map1.png?t=1735796284\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge yourself to beat the best times on endless player-created maps, or just have fun exploring and overcoming unique levels at your own pace. Fancy a bit of friendly competition? Share your creations with the world, challenge your friends to complete your custom-designed maps, or take on their wildest creations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/Gameplay2.png?t=1735796284\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Arcade Galaxy</strong>, you can customize your <i>Cubs</i> to match your unique style. Choose from a vast array of cosmetics and abilities to create a look and playstyle that\u2019s truly your own. This rich customization ensures every player can build a game experience that reflects their personality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/2.png?t=1735796284\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Create. Share. Challenge.</strong> Whether you\u2019re building epic levels, breaking records, or sharing laughs with friends, <strong>Arcade Galaxy</strong> is your ticket to endless intergalactic fun. Jump in today and start shaping the universe! \ud83d\ude80 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83d\udd79\ufe0f Endless Challenges:</strong> Play and compete on an ever-growing library of player-made levels. Beat records, or set your own! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/GamePlay1.gif?t=1735796284\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 <strong>\ud83c\udf0c Build Your Vision:</strong> Design levels with robust tools and customize every detail, from terrain to gameplay mechanics. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/Builder.gif?t=1735796284\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83c\udf0e Share Your World:</strong> Publish your creations and challenge the global community to conquer your designs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/GamePlay2.gif?t=1735796284\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83c\udfa8 Customize Your Cubs:</strong> Personalize your Cubs with a galaxy of cosmetics and abilities to make them truly 